text.section:
If the property of the applicant is in the departmental inspection area, before issuing a permit, the Secretary shall inspect the property, buildings, and equipment of an applicant for:
A bobtailer permit;
A distribution station permit;
A milk processor permit;
A milk processor - farmstead cheese producer permit;
A milk producer permit;
A milk transportation company permit;
A receiving station permit; or
A transfer station permit.
